node.text: You guys!!! I’ve been wanting to share my 5 minute makeup routine for a while and I finally got around to doing it. It involves a little bit of dancing around and I would say the most time-consuming part of it is looking for all the products I can’t find but I hope it’s helpful to all of you ❤️ ——————— * Damp beauty blender with Laura Mercier tinted moisturizer w SPF 25 in shade 4W1 mixed with Koh Gen Do moisturize foundation in 003 because I’m a little tan right now * Laura Mercier flawless fusion ultra-longwear concealer in 2C for under eyes *Lumify eye drops for brightening eyes * Cle De Peau concealer in almond for any dark spots * Eye lash curl!!! My favorite step * Charlotte tilbury filmstar bronze and glow bronzer in fair-medium for bronzer * Charlotte tilbury filmstar bronze and glow bronzer in medium-dark as eye shadow. I loveeee this trick!

I could go on and on. You are my soul sister and I’m grateful for you forever and always. You deserve everything your heart desires today and every day! ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️ (the last pic here just really hits different 😂😭😂)

node.text: First time in Greece and the best part is having these two with me. When they got here yesterday my energy completed shifted and I felt at home. My heart is so full and they just make me the luckiest girl in the world (even when they’re being savage + sassy 🥴). Just a little reminder that family is absolutely everything ❤️🥺 @auroraculpo @sophiaculpo
